              <p class="text-on-surface-variant group-hover:text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-sm">Formerly of Global Systems, Elena leads our long-term strategic vision and governance.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group bg-white p-12 transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-[#1A36B0] hover:-translate-y-1">
              <div class="mb-8 overflow-hidden grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500">
                <img class="w-full aspect-square object-cover rounded-full p-2 border border-outline-variant group-hover:border-white/20" data-alt="Minimalist professional studio portrait of a man in a navy turtleneck, high-end corporate style, neutral background" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAif9CySrtdCj6VIQn-J3jAV-VsW18JwXyghb0JiMTr-PZxEoZ9XyWa6zOsyqurqJjYYQj03tyZ7RcLmrIBNJfKNJ163iwoV16iOKtqQG3XfwIgdWrfCrYN3Da44nB20Zm9zZIXtdxiXCY8qF8CaZZO-Y5Yd6AJNhFNu6L5BeL8iuhaltX5vCT9oAv6trwXhAsnP9r-6RJmwggpJb-KXBEDX3h54Z50eq-aX9n6BKmrH2b6SsSBWMWgpjwQqMaaDkUMSJ-gVCjSJDp5" />
              </div>
              <h4 class="text-2xl font-headline font-medium mb-1 group-hover:text-white">Marcus Thorne</h4>
              <p class="text-primary font-medium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 group-hover:text-white/80">Chief Technology Officer</p>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant group-hover:text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-sm">A pioneer in distributed systems, Marcus oversees all architectural innovations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group bg-white p-12 transition-all duration-500 hover:bg-[#1A36B0] hover:-translate-y-1">
              <div class="mb-8 overflow-hidden grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500">
